name King Armewir
msg
@match hi|hello
Welcome to my feast! Have a seat! 
@match quest|Quest|dwarves|
Those fool dwarves stole my best
crown,now I have to wear this ugly one.
Do you think you can retrieve it for me?
@match yes
Good! Go to the dwarven kingdom and
bring back the crown. Just drop it on
my table.
@match woods|dark wood|monsters
Yes,the monsters. They are dangerous to
my people,but they keep away intruders.
My last visit from intruders was a week
ago. Seven dwarves came and stole my
crown. They had a gnomish magician with
them. They escaped through an
underground river.

endmsg
